&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;line-numbers&#34;&gt;#n::Run D:\Program Files\MarkdownPicPicker_v1.0.0\MarkdownPicPicker_v1.0.0\MarkdownPicPicker.exe -linkonly
